Day 18:
Step 0: Log in to the Azure Portal (https://portal.azure.com/).


_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________


1. Create and Configure User Accounts:

Step 1: Navigate to Microsoft Entra ID in menu bar [Located in top left corner of home] (or) you can search Microssoft Entra ID in Search bar.
Step 2: In Overview, go to MANAGE TENANTS.
Step 3: Return to Entra ID page.
Step 4: Select Lisecenses.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---> Create a new User:
Step 1: Select new Users in Entra ID menu and click on CREATE NEW USER.
Step 2: Enter the necessary details: 
        a. User pricipal name
        b. Display name
        c. Account generate password
        d. Account enabled
        e. Job title
        f. Usage Location
Step 3: Then click on CREATE when you go to review + create.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---> Invite an External User:
Step 1: Select new Users in Entra ID menu and click on CREATE NEW USER.
Step 2: Enter the necessary details: 
        a. e-mail address
        b. Display name
        c. Send invite message
        d. Description
        e. Message
        f. Job title
        g. Usage Location
Step 3: Then click on CREATE when you go to review + invite.

____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________


2. Create Groups and add Members:
Step 1: Navigate to Microsoft Entra ID in menu bar [Located in top left corner of home] (or) you can search Microssoft Entra ID in Search bar.
Step 2: In Overview, go to Groups and select it.
Step 3: Select "+new group" and enter the necessary details: 
        a. Group type - security
        b. Group name
        c. Group description
        d. Membership type
        e. No memebers - selected
Step 4: In add Members, search for and select the guest user you invited via e-mail.
Step 5: Select create to deploy the Group.
Step 6: Select the Groups and review it.


